##  By default, we *view* and *display* vector objects and matrix objects as
##  '<vector object of length ... over ...>' and
##  '<matrix object of dimensions ... over ...>', respectively,
##  and to *print* them as 'NewVector( ... )' and 'NewMatrix( ... )',
